Trubbish (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0567: Archeops
Pokémon
#0569: Garbodor →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Trubbish (TCG Pocket).

Trubbish has been featured on 12 different cards since it debuted in the Noble Victories expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Trubbish cards are normally Darkness-type Basic Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Trubbish

Trubbish
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
